channel.title: Project Insanity Commands don't work?
channel.description: Well i have been trying to use many different PI sources, and on most of them, most of the commands don't work. I would like to know how to fix it. EX: ::item doesn't work at all. I'm used to delta and was wondering if the "rights" system is different and maybe that's why it's not working.
